      "instruction": "<p>Once the aubergine is tender, add your <strong>cultured coconut </strong>and <strong>rice vinegar</strong> to the pan and stir everything together</p><p>Add the <strong>drained noodles </strong>with the<strong> reserved starchy noodle water</strong></p><p>Mix everything together<strong> </strong>until the noodles are fully coated and cook for a final 2-3 min or until the sauce has slightly thickened – these are your <strong>coconutty curried aubergine noodles</strong></p>",
